{"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PSReaderUI"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Getting Started"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide walks you through installation, credentials, SDK initialization, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"launching your first reader experience. By the end you will have a working"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselViewController","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" displaying your publication editions."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Installation","text":"Installation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We support three installation methods for integrating the SDK into your iOS app:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Manual installation","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"CocoaPods"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift Package Manager (SPM)","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Access to our CocoaPods Specs repository and Swift Package repository is "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"private","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" and granted via SSH."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To request access, please generate an SSH key pair and send the public key to our team. We’ll provision access to the appropriate repositories."}]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"1-Manual-Installation","text":"1. Manual Installation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Manually install the provided ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PSReaderUI.xcframework"},{"text":" and its dependencies by dragging and dropping them into your Xcode project.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"PSReaderUI.xcframework","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"PSReader.xcframework","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"PDFNet.xcframework"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tools.xcframework"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Ensure the frameworks are set to "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Embed and Sign"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" in your Xcode project settings."}]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","text":"2. CocoaPods","level":3,"anchor":"2-CocoaPods"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Specs repository:"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["git@bitbucket.org:pagesuite\/psreader-specs.git"]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The Apryse SDK integration is slightly non-standard. We recommend pinning it to version "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"11.6.0.85755"},{"type":"text","text":", as this is the version we have tested internally."}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Podfile"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"ruby","code":["source 'git@bitbucket.org:pagesuite\/psreader-specs.git'","","target 'YourAppTarget' do","  use_frameworks!","","  pod 'PDFTron', podspec: 'https:\/\/www.pdftron.com\/downloads\/ios\/cocoapods\/xcframeworks\/pdftron\/11.3.0.85075.podspec'","  pod 'PDFTronTools', podspec: 'https:\/\/www.pdftron.com\/downloads\/ios\/cocoapods\/xcframeworks\/pdftron-tools\/11.3.0.85075.podspec'","  pod 'PSReaderUI2'","end"]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","text":"3. Swift Package Manager","level":3,"anchor":"3-Swift-Package-Manager"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Package URL:"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"syntax":null,"code":["git@bitbucket.org:pagesuite\/psreader-swift-package.git"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To integrate:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In Xcode, go to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"File > Add Packages…","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Enter the repository URL above.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Authenticate via SSH (make sure you have been granted access)."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Select the desired version\/range and add the package to your target.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"text":"Versioning","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Versioning"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Starting in 2026, the SDK uses a calendar-based versioning scheme to align"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the rest of the PageSuite product line. Versions follow the format"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"year.month.patch","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" — for example, "},{"code":"26.1.0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the first January 2026"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"release."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This scheme does ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"not","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" follow semantic versioning. While we strive to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"maintain API stability, breaking changes may occur in any release without a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"major version bump. We recommend pinning to a specific version and reviewing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Change-Log","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" before upgrading.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Credentials","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Credentials"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To use the PSReaderUI SDK you need the following credentials. Contact your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"PageSuite account manager or check the PageSuite portal to obtain them.","type":"text"}]},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Credential"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"API Key"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Authenticates your app with the PageSuite backend.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Account GUID"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Identifies your account."}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Shortcode","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" (recommended)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A short identifier that maps to your publication configuration. Use with ","type":"text"},{"code":".dynamicArchive","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to load content automatically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Application GUID","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Identifies a specific feed edition publication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Publication GUID"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Identifies a specific replica publication."}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Shortcode is the recommended approach."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" It lets the SDK fetch your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"publication configuration dynamically, so you don’t need to manage GUIDs","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"yourself.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"tip","name":"Tip"},{"text":"Initialize the SDK","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Initialize-the-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The PSReader SDK must be globally initialized before it can be used. Call this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method early in your app lifecycle to optimize reader launch speed. You only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"need to call this method once."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The completion handler is only used to return a status flag. It is not required"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and it is not necessary to wait for the completion handler before continuing."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method will only fail if the API key is invalid.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import PSReaderUI","","PSReader.initialize(apiKey: apiKey, completion: { success in","    \/\/ Note: The completion handler may be called on any thread.","})"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Quick Start","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Quick-Start"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Create a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/GlobalConfiguration","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" with your credentials and basic theming:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import PSReaderUI","","let globalConfig = PSReaderUI.GlobalConfiguration(","    apiKey: apiKey,","    accountGUID: accountGUID,","    primaryFont: .systemFont(ofSize: 12),","    secondaryFont: .systemFont(ofSize: 12),","    brandColor: UIColor(dynamicProvider: {","        $0.userInterfaceStyle == .dark ? .white : .black","    })",")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The primary font is used for titles, headlines, and publication names. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"secondary font covers the remaining UI. The brand color is used as an accent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"throughout the SDK."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then create a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselViewController","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" using a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"shortcode"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":".dynamicArchive","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let carouselVC = PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController(","    globalConfig: globalConfig,","    sections: [","        .dynamicArchive(\"Editions\", shortcode: \"SHORTCODE\"),","        .subsections(\"My Content\", [","            .init(name: \"Bookmarks\", type: .bookmarks(type: .all)),","            .init(name: \"Downloads\", type: .downloads(type: .all))","        ])","    ]",")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can now push, present, or embed the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CarouselViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" as needed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Carousel-Setup","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for more detail on sections, content types, and layout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"options."}]},{"text":"Manual Configuration","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Manual-Configuration"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to use explicit GUIDs instead of a shortcode, replace","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".dynamicArchive"},{"text":" with a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".section"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".subsections"},{"text":" entry using the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"appropriate content type:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Feed edition archive with an application GUID",".section(.init(name: \"Editions\", type: .feedArchive(guid: \"APP_GUID\")))","","\/\/ Replica archive with a publication GUID",".section(.init(name: \"Editions\", type: .replicaArchive(guid: \"PUB_GUID\")))"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/Replica-and-Feed-Editions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to determine which content type matches"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"your publication."}]},{"text":"Dark Mode","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Dark-Mode"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK fully supports dark mode. To provide distinct light and dark brand"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors, use a dynamic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIColor"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let brandColor = UIColor(dynamicProvider: {","    $0.userInterfaceStyle == .dark ? .white : .black","})"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, define a color in your asset catalog so the system resolves it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"automatically."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To force a specific appearance across the entire SDK, set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"overrideUserInterfaceStyle","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselViewController","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["carouselVC.overrideUserInterfaceStyle = .dark"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Embedding in SwiftUI","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Embedding-in-SwiftUI"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Wrap the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselViewController","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" in a ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIViewControllerRepresentable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use it in a SwiftUI view hierarchy:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import SwiftUI","import PSReaderUI","","struct ReaderView: UIViewControllerRepresentable {","    func makeUIViewController(context: Context) -> PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController {","        let globalConfig = PSReaderUI.GlobalConfiguration(","            apiKey: \"API_KEY\",","            accountGUID: \"ACCOUNT_GUID\"","        )","        return PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController(","            globalConfig: globalConfig,","            sections: [","                .dynamicArchive(\"Editions\", shortcode: \"SHORTCODE\")","            ]","        )","    }","","    func updateUIViewController(_ uiViewController: PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController, context: Context) {}","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Using a Coordinator as a Delegate","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Using-a-Coordinator-as-a-Delegate"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK makes wide use of delegate protocols (see "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/GlobalConfiguration","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When embedding in SwiftUI, you can implement delegates on a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Coordinator"},{"type":"text","text":" so their"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lifecycle is tied to the representable:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct ReaderView: UIViewControllerRepresentable {","    func makeCoordinator() -> Coordinator {","        Coordinator()","    }","","    func makeUIViewController(context: Context) -> PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController {","        let globalConfig = PSReaderUI.GlobalConfiguration(","            apiKey: \"API_KEY\",","            accountGUID: \"ACCOUNT_GUID\",","            navigationDelegate: context.coordinator","        )","        return PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController(","            globalConfig: globalConfig,","            sections: [","                .dynamicArchive(\"Editions\", shortcode: \"SHORTCODE\")","            ]","        )","    }","","    func updateUIViewController(_ uiViewController: PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController, context: Context) {}","","    class Coordinator: NavigationDelegate {","        func willPresentReplicaReader() {","            \/\/ Track analytics, adjust UI state, etc.","        }","","        func willDismissReplicaReader() {","            \/\/ Restore UI state, etc.","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The same approach works for any delegate — have "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Coordinator"},{"text":" conform to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/PaywallDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/ShareDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", or any combination you need and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"pass ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"context.coordinator"},{"type":"text","text":" to the corresponding "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GlobalConfiguration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameter."}]},{"text":"Presenting Modally","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Presenting-Modally"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When presenting the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pagesuite.PSReaderUI\/documentation\/PSReaderUI\/CarouselViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" modally, add a dismiss button"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so users can close it:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["var carouselConfig = PSReaderUI.CarouselConfiguration(globalConfig: globalConfig)","carouselConfig.dismissButton = .dismissButton(position: .leading())","","let carouselVC = PSReaderUI.CarouselViewController(","    globalConfig: globalConfig,","    carouselConfig: carouselConfig,","    sections: [ \/* ... *\/ ]",")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you are embedding the carousel inside your own ","type":"text"},{"code":"UINavigationController","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"set ","type":"text"},{"code":"embedInNavigationController","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the carousel configuration","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to prevent the SDK from creating a second navigation controller, which would","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"result in double navigation bars:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["carouselConfig.embedInNavigationController = false"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"App Store Compliance","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"App-Store-Compliance"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Export Compliance"}]}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK does "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"not","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" use any non-standard encryption and will not affect export controls."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Privacy Compliance","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK does "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"not","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" collect any private information and will not affect privacy compliance."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Required Info.plist Keys","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK uses the Apryse library to render PDFs, which is preferred over Core"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Graphics for its closer adherence to PDF standards. Add the following keys to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"your app’s "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info.plist"}]},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For more information, see the Apryse documentation:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.apryse.com\/ios\/guides\/get-started\/integration?tab=spm","isActive":true}]},{"syntax":"xml","code":["<k